asset.hookText:
Hi. We saw your review on our site. We think we might know what's causing your Hoover WindTunnel T-Series Pet Rewind not picking up well on carpet. We put together a quick video to help you get it working properly again. Let us know if you need any more help! -Amber

EDITED: We put together a quick video to show you how to take the hose off. You can see it here: http://youtu.be/CyEQpPz-1YI
